00:42:00,119 --> 00:42:01,530
Hey, Rusty.

516
00:42:01,663 --> 00:42:03,573
Hey, wait... Wait a minute.

517
00:42:03,707 --> 00:42:05,250
Hey, Rusty, come on.

518
00:42:05,377 --> 00:42:09,625
