529
00:42:55,533 --> 00:42:56,862
<i>... on opposing players.</i>

530
00:42:56,994 --> 00:42:58,738
<i>Yeah, fine.</i>

531
00:42:58,872 --> 00:43:01,245
We want you to approve the sequences.

532
00:43:01,459 --> 00:43:05,043
<i>It's, uh... It's all fine with me. Uh...</i>

533
00:43:06,258 --> 00:43:07,254
<i>Anything.</i>

534
00:43:07,384 --> 00:43:10,552
I really... don't see why I'm needed here.

535
00:43:10,764 --> 00:43:13,885
<i>Well, the Energy people</i>
<i>want you to be satisfied.</i>

536
00:43:14,019 --> 00:43:16,594
<i>There, now. Isn't that a marvellous shot?</i>

537
00:43:19,151 --> 00:43:20,148
Sure.

538
00:43:20,278 --> 00:43:23,696
<i>I'm a stat freak myself. Isn't that perverse?</i>

539
00:43:24,034 --> 00:43:26,074
Have you got anything I can take?

540
00:43:28,415 --> 00:43:30,456
Just, uh, just take one, huh?

541
00:43:32,045 --> 00:43:32,995
Statistics, huh?

542
00:43:33,130 --> 00:43:37,046
<i>Yes, the greatest number of points</i>
<i>scored in a single game, 18.</i>

543
00:43:37,178 --> 00:43:41,723
<i>The highest velocity of a ball when</i>
<i>actually fielded by a skater, 120mph.</i>

544
00:43:41,851 --> 00:43:43,050
<i>Most deaths...</i>

545
00:43:43,187 --> 00:43:45,264
- <i>(feedback)</i>
