570
00:44:53,248 --> 00:44:55,657
- Feeling woozy?
- <i>Just try to read the announcement.</i>

571
00:44:55,793 --> 00:44:57,834
I'm all right.

572
00:44:59,257 --> 00:45:01,630
Why don't you... read...

573
00:45:01,760 --> 00:45:02,757
...the...

574
00:45:02,887 --> 00:45:04,928
Oh, yeah, you want that, do you?

575
00:45:05,057 --> 00:45:07,097
<i>You are making things difficult.</i>

576
00:45:07,227 --> 00:45:10,597
How many, uh, how many assignments
you been on, Daph?

577
00:45:12,359 --> 00:45:14,898
Oh, you're good at what you're good at...

578
00:45:15,030 --> 00:45:17,070
...so you must have been around some.

579
00:45:17,200 --> 00:45:20,036
A lot of girls have stayed with me.
You know that.

580
00:45:20,162 --> 00:45:22,203
Never seemed to mind.

581
00:45:23,042 --> 00:45:24,750
But odd thoughts...

582
00:45:24,878 --> 00:45:27,251
...I've had about you, Daph. Odd thoughts.

583
00:45:27,381 --> 00:45:29,671
Wondered if you'd been briefed on me.

584
00:45:29,802 --> 00:45:31,261
<i>I'll ask you to read...</i>

585
00:45:31,387 --> 00:45:35,303
Yeah, a lot of things occur to me, Daph.
A lot of things occur to you?

586
00:45:38,314 --> 00:45:40,723
You look terrible.

587
00:45:40,859 --> 00:45:42,900
You do look terrible.

588
00:45:43,739 --> 00:45:45,779
Come on.

589
00:45:47,369 --> 00:45:48,698
<i>(soundtrack)</i>

590
00:45:48,829 --> 00:45:52,117
You shouldn't take anything
offered to you just like that.

591
00:45:52,251 --> 00:45:54,043
What was in it?

592
00:45:54,171 --> 00:45:58,253
Nothing to hurt you.
You're too trusting. Ever think of that?

593
00:45:58,385 --> 00:46:00,426
<i>(crowd cheering)</i>

594
00:46:21,794 --> 00:46:23,170
Hook 'em deep now!

595
00:46:36,358 --> 00:46:39,111
They're good boys, but they're a bit rough.

596
00:46:40,614 --> 00:46:42,654
Thank you.

597
00:46:49,335 --> 00:46:52,456
As you know, the Tokyo game is coming up.

598
00:46:53,049 --> 00:46:55,837
And you will remember that the Tokyo team...

599
00:46:55,970 --> 00:46:59,305
...uses various karate and Hapkido techniques.

600
00:46:59,433 --> 00:47:01,806
