606
00:47:19,546 --> 00:47:20,542
<i>(laughter)</i>

607
00:47:20,965 --> 00:47:23,373
Especially in a game with no penalties and...

608
00:47:23,510 --> 00:47:28,008
You gotta get mad, all right? Play hard.
It don't matter if they're all tiny little men.

609
00:47:28,142 --> 00:47:32,188
Especially in a game with no penalties
and limited substitutions.

610
00:47:32,315 --> 00:47:34,355
Get mad and fly!

611
00:47:35,027 --> 00:47:36,023
Please...

612
00:47:36,279 --> 00:47:38,818
There are certain body areas
that I know about, too.

613
00:47:38,949 --> 00:47:41,442
What we gotta do is hit those guys
in the ganglia.

614
00:47:41,578 --> 00:47:42,492
Where?

615
00:47:42,621 --> 00:47:46,122
In the ganglia. That's a mess of nerves
right here under the ear.

616
00:47:46,252 --> 00:47:50,298
You gotta drive the jawbone up in that
mess of nerves, and it rings a bell.

617
00:47:50,425 --> 00:47:51,588
<i>(laughter)</i>

618
00:47:51,718 --> 00:47:53,759
You must understand...

619
00:47:53,888 --> 00:47:58,137
...the Tokyo team
has a very eccentric playing style.

620
00:47:58,269 --> 00:48:01,972
And no penalties! If I go down,
I know my team is with me, right?

621
00:48:02,108 --> 00:48:02,689
Please.

622
00:48:02,818 --> 00:48:04,099
Brute speed!

623
00:48:04,237 --> 00:48:07,737
Familiarise yourself with
the basic fighting-art techniques.

624
00:48:07,867 --> 00:48:10,276
Nobody's gonna take us, rules or no rules.

625
00:48:10,412 --> 00:48:11,112
Go on.

626
00:48:11,247 --> 00:48:13,324
This is the Houston team!

627
00:48:13,458 --> 00:48:16,330
- Rules or no rules.
